With the year nearing an end, I am announcing that I am no longer tattooing at Under The Gun. I am beyond grateful for the past 7 years I have spent here and all the memories I’ve shared. UTG has created a home for me, a brotherhood and friendships that will last a lifetime. Thank you @chente_rios for giving me this huge opportunity to be an artist at your shop.. this was something I use to dream about! I always tell people there’s a magic about UTG. The energy here is different! It really has been an honor working here. I’m blessed. Thank you to all my family and friends and ofcourse my clientele for supporting me through out the years and watching me grow into what I am today. Thank you to the UTG team for all the good times that I’ll never forget. Cheers to new ventures and the new chapter!
Happy New Year and Much love❤️ @utgtattoo.co 
#UTG #UnderTheGun
